creator: Westbury Bank
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy banking on the go! All of our essential financial services are now available for Apple, Android, Windows and select Blackberry devices. With our App you can easily and securely view balances, schedule payments, transfer funds and much more! This service requires enrollment in our FREE online banking system. Please go to www.westburybankwi.com to sign up, then simply register for mobile banking, download the app and login using your online credentials.

* View Balances and history
* Transfer funds with ease between westbury bank accounts
* Make deposits
* Pay or schedule payments conveniently through the Bill Payment features
* Pay or schedule person-to-person (P2P) payments using PopMoney
* Locate ATM/Branches wherever you are based on the location information you enter

The westbury mobile App is FREE to download, although your mobile carrier's message and data rates may apply. Check with your carrier for specific fees and charges. Any fees associated with transactions will be identified during usage.
